Privacy and Policy
Welcome to Travel Animator, your top companion for creating awe-inspiring videos of your journeys for social media. This Privacy and Policy document outlines our commitment to safeguarding your privacy, detailing the types of information we collect, how we use it, and under what circumstances, if any, we disclose it.
Personal Information:
Travel Animator respects your privacy. We do not collect or store any personal identifiable information such as email addresses or phone numbers, as our app does not require users to log in.
Non-Personal Information:
While we don't collect personal information, we do gather non-personal data to enhance user experience. This includes:
App usage statistics
Properties of created videos (e.g., duration, selected options)
Subscription plan details
The non-personal information we collect serves the following purposes:
Operational Efficiency:
To ensure seamless app functionality and improve user experience.
Subscription Management:
To manage and keep track of our users' subscription plans, ensuring timely renewals and addressing any related concerns.
Legal Obligations:
To comply with any applicable laws and regulations.
Travel Animator values your trust. We do not share, sell, or disclose your information to third parties, except:
When required by law.
If the organization undergoes a merger, acquisition, or asset sale.
We prioritize the security of our users' information. While no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, we employ robust security measures to prevent unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of your non-personal information.
Travel Animator uses cookies to enhance user experience by remembering preferences and repeat visits. By using our app, you consent to the use of these cookies. However, these cookies do not store any personal identifiable information.
As a user of Travel Animator:
Subscription Management:
You have the right to manage, renew, or cancel your subscription at any time.
Information Inquiry:
While we don't collect personal data, you can always inquire about the non-personal data we have.
Feedback:
We welcome any feedback or concerns related to your privacy.
Our Privacy and Policy may evolve over time. We will notify users of any significant changes through in-app notifications or other appropriate channels. We recommend reviewing this policy periodically.
For any inquiries, feedback, or concerns related to this Privacy and Policy, please reach out to us through our official website.